Package com.edugility.nomen

Provides classes and interfaces for working with names of all varieties.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Named An owner of Names that can retrieve them efficiently when asked for them by NameType.
Valued Indicates that an implementation is capable of reporting its value as a String.
 

Class Summary
AbstractNamed A skeletal implementation of the Named interface, together with mutator methods.
AbstractValued A Serializable Valued implementation that correctly implements the AbstractValued.equals(Object) and AbstractValued.hashCode() methods.
Name A Serializable AbstractValued implementation that is a combination of a NameValue and the Named that it is currently assigned to.
NameType An AbstractValued implementation that serves as a key within a Named to identify particular Name instances.
NameValue An AbstractValued implementation that represents the value of a name of something.
 

Package com.edugility.nomen Description

Provides classes and interfaces for working with names of all varieties.
